{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>K-pop Idol Stories: Road to Debut</strong> is a love letter to the thrilling world of K-pop!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this life simulator, you're the manager responsible for scouting talent, managing schedules, creating budgets, planning social media, choosing music, and styling your idols.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   Your goal? To debut the next big K-pop idol group!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Choose Your Trainees</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/KISS_GIF_steamstore_trainees.gif?t=1734615655\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each trainee has unique characteristics and a backstory.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">One girl might have fierce confidence that drives fans wild but could also disrupt the group dynamic.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Another might be a shy songbird who needs a little encouragement to shine\u2014how will she handle the spotlight when she\u2019s ready for the stage?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As their manager, it's up to you to understand their stories, personalities, and strengths. Assemble a diverse and dynamic group of idols to create the perfect team!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Original K-pop Soundtrack</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/KISS_GIF_steamstore_song.gif?t=1734615655\" />What\u2019s your K-pop group\u2019s concept? Choose the soundtrack for their debut single, produced by a K-pop composer exclusively for this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Your Choices Matter</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/KISS_GIF_steamstore_relationship.gif?t=1734615655\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What kind of manager are you? Disciplined and straightforward, or caring and compassionate?</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you prioritise pleasing the label's board members?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you always be honest with your trainees, or keep certain things secret until debut day?</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The choice is yours.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Unlock and Plan Schedules</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/KISS_GIF_steamstore_schedule.gif?t=1734615655\" />Should you send your idols to rigorous dance practice, or let them unwind with a relaxing yoga class? Your choices impact the team\u2019s growth and the story\u2019s direction.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/steam_lineUpCharSept24.png?t=1734615655\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734615655","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/page.bg.jpg?t=1734615655","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/987be0a21f937e4e874c6597afc1764997766d00/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734615655","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/987be0a21f937e4e874c6597afc1764997766d00/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734615655","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":51},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"Remote Play on TV","id":43}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"no